{
  "stem": "3341.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then these young people are going for forced labor, because the propaganda of Germany was always that the Jews are not first to be equal, because they use the non-Jewish public, and they use swindles, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it would be time, or it is the time ripe then Jews should start to work hard for their living.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I come to that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That happens from '39, because in '39 is, you know, Germany declared war against Russia-- against Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the beginning of the World War II.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Czechoslovakia was already divided, from March until the war started-- about July, October-- against Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the tough anti-Jewish laws were introduced mainly from that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Gradually they built up to 1941, to such extents and in '42, were the first transports there, [? actually. ?] The very first transport was the young boys and young girls. 2,000 they took from Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were taking many more from their country, I guess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I volunteered, that is the silly thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1939, when I came home-- in '38 and '39 I was already home-- the-- I was called to the army as a active service, because we had two years active service to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my two brothers, the older one and the middle one were already in the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were called to the two years active service.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there is an unwritten law everywhere, in every country, if a family has two children, two sons in the army, the third one does not need to go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you have to ask for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I didn't ask, and my parents had lots of other worries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't worry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day, I-- my year was called up, and I went.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
